# Header Design System Rules

This document defines the design system rules for the header section of the Investors Hub Landing Page ONLY, based on the Figma design specifications.

## Layout & Structure

### Container
- **Max Width**: `1200px` (centered)
- **Horizontal Padding**: `83px` on both sides
- **Structure**: Two-tier header layout
  - Top utility bar (profile & settings)
  - Main navigation bar

### Header Hierarchy
```
Header (Fixed/Sticky)
├── Top Utility Bar (36px height)
│   ├── Left Section: Language + Settings
│   └── Right Section: User Actions
└── Main Navigation Bar (69px height)
    ├── Left Section: Logo
    └── Right Section: Navigation Items + CTA Button
```

## Colors

### Background Colors
- **Top Bar Background**: `#000000` (solid black)
- **Main Navigation Background**: `rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)` (50% transparent black overlay)
- **Primary CTA Button**: `#28b16d` (bayut green)
- **Badge Background**: `#ff3d16` (urgent red)

### Text Colors
- **Primary Text**: `#FFFFFF` (pure white)
- **Secondary Text**: `#E6E6E6` (light grey)
- **Button Text**: `#FFFFFF` (white)
- **Badge Text**: `#FFFFFF` (white)

### Border Colors
- **Divider Line**: `rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.15)` (15% opacity white)
- Applied as bottom border on top utility bar

## Typography

### Font Family
- **Primary Font**: `Lato, sans-serif`
- **Font Weights**:
  - Regular: 400 (default navigation items)
  - Semibold: 600 (CTA button text)
  - Bold: 700 (featured navigation items, "Log in" text)

### Font Sizes & Line Heights
- **Top Utility Bar**: 
  - Size: `14px`
  - Line Height: `14px` (1:1 ratio)
  
- **Main Navigation Items**: 
  - Size: `16px`
  - Line Height: `16px` (1:1 ratio)
  
- **Badge Text**: 
  - Size: `8px`
  - Line Height: `7.765px`
  - Letter Spacing: `0.48px` (uppercase text)

## Spacing System

### Vertical Spacing
- **Top Bar Height**: `36px` total
  - Padding Y: `9px` top/bottom
  - Content Height: `18px`

- **Main Navigation Height**: `69px` total
  - Padding Top: `16px`
  - Padding Bottom: `15px`
  - Content Height: `32px` (logo height)

### Horizontal Spacing
- **Container Side Padding**: `83px`
- **Navigation Item Gaps**: 
  - Small: `22px` (between most nav items)
  - Medium: `32px` (before special nav items)
  - Large: `16px` (top bar user actions)
- **Internal Component Spacing**:
  - Icon-to-text gap: `8px`
  - Badge gap: `4.853px`

### Element-Specific Spacing
- **Logo**:
  - Width: `125px`
  - Height: `32px`
  - Right margin: `16px`

- **Icons**:
  - Size: `18px × 18px`
  - Right margin: `8px` (when preceding text)

