- **Layout**: Text + Down Arrow
- **Arrow Icon**: `9px × 14px`
- **Gap**: `6px` between text and arrow
- **Dropdown Position**: Below, left-aligned
- **Dropdown Background**: `#FFFFFF` (white)
- **Dropdown Shadow**: `0 4px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15)`

## Responsive Behavior

### Breakpoints (Recommended)
- **Desktop**: `1366px` and above (full layout)
- **Tablet**: `768px - 1365px` (adjusted spacing)
- **Mobile**: Below `768px` (hamburger menu)

### Desktop (≥ 1366px)
- Full header layout as designed
- All navigation items visible
- Container padding: `83px`

### Tablet (768px - 1365px)
- Reduce container padding to `24px`
- Maintain two-tier structure
- Consider hiding some utility items

### Mobile (< 768px)
- Collapse to hamburger menu
- Show only logo and menu icon
- Height: `56px` (reduced)
- Menu icon: `24px × 24px`

## Accessibility

### ARIA Labels
- Logo: `aria-label="Home"`
- Navigation: `<nav role="navigation" aria-label="Main navigation">`
- User menu: `aria-label="User account menu"`
- Language switcher: `aria-label="Change language"`

### Keyboard Navigation
- All interactive elements must be keyboard accessible
- Tab order: Left to right, top to bottom
- Focus indicators: `outline: 2px solid #28b16d`
- Focus offset: `outline-offset: 2px`

### Color Contrast
- **White on Black**: 21:1 (WCAG AAA) ✓
- **#E6E6E6 on Black**: 16.2:1 (WCAG AAA) ✓
- **White on #28b16d**: 2.63:1 (requires icon or bold text for AA)
- **White on #ff3d16**: 3.28:1 (WCAG AA for large text) ✓

## States & Interactions

### Link Hover States
```css
Default: color: #E6E6E6
Hover: color: #FFFFFF
Active: color: #FFFFFF, opacity: 0.8
```

### Button Hover States
```css
Default: background: #28b16d
Hover: background: #239f5f, transform: translateY(-1px)
Active: background: #1e8a52, transform: translateY(0)
Focus: outline: 2px solid #28b16d, outline-offset: 2px
```

### Dropdown Interactions
- **Trigger**: Click or hover (choose one for consistency)
- **Animation**: Fade in + slide down (200ms ease-out)
- **Close**: Click outside or click trigger again
- **Overlay**: Semi-transparent backdrop on mobile

## Z-Index Hierarchy
```
Header Container: z-index: 1000
  └── Dropdown Menu: z-index: 1001
  └── Mobile Menu: z-index: 1002
Badge (NEW): z-index: 1 (relative to parent)
```

## Performance Considerations

### Image Optimization
- Logo: SVG (< 5KB)
- Icons: SVG sprite sheet or icon font
- Background images: WebP format with PNG fallback

### Loading Strategy
- Header: Above the fold (critical CSS)
- Icons: Preload critical icons
- Fonts: Use `font-display: swap` for Lato

## Animation Specifications

### Transitions
- **Link Hover**: `color 200ms ease-in-out`
- **Button Hover**: `background 200ms ease-in-out, transform 150ms ease-out`
- **Dropdown Open**: `opacity 200ms ease-out, transform 200ms ease-out`
- **Mobile Menu**: `transform 300ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1)`

### Transforms
- **Button Hover**: `translateY(-1px)`
- **Dropdown**: `translateY(8px)` to `translateY(0)`

